flowchart LR
    Client([Guest / Host])
    Search[Search Service<br/>geo + filters]
    Listing[Listing Service]
    Booking[Booking Orchestrator<br/>Saga]
    Calendar[Calendar Service<br/>per-listing per-night]
    Payment[Payment Service<br/>escrow]
    Notify[Notification Service]
    SearchIdx[(Search Index<br/>denormalized)]
    ListingsDB[(Listings DB<br/>transactional)]

    Client -->|search| Search
    Client -->|browse| Listing
    Client -->|book| Booking
    Search --> SearchIdx
    Listing --> ListingsDB
    ListingsDB -.->|CDC| SearchIdx
    Booking -->|lock dates| Calendar
    Booking --> Payment
    Booking -.-> Notify
    Notify -.->|host + guest| Client

    classDef external fill:#1e2533,stroke:#3a4a6e,color:#cfd6e6
    classDef service fill:#1a3a2e,stroke:#3a6e54,color:#cfe6d6
    classDef store fill:#1e2a3e,stroke:#3a5a8e,color:#cfdcef
    classDef config fill:#3a2e1a,stroke:#6e5a3a,color:#efdfcf

    class Client external
    class Search,Listing,Booking,Calendar,Payment,Notify service
    class SearchIdx,ListingsDB store
